   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the two plates in the bottom of the UPS cabinet.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View of the UPS Cabinet</title>
                  <image href="../Images/50_kva_connect_power_cables_remove_plates_120mm_0000104238.svg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         translate="no"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the three input busbars from the unit input breaker
UIB. Save the three busbar screws.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the three busbar screws from the static switch input
breaker SSIB. Save the three busbar screws.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View of the UPS Cabinet</title>
                  <image href="../Images/50_kva_convert_from_dual_mains_to_single_mains_remove_the_input_busbars_120mm_-_copy_0000110491.svg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Install the provided busbar assembly for single mains between
the unit input breaker UIB and the static switch input breaker SSIB
and fasten with the six busbar screws removed in earlier steps.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View of the UPS Cabinet</title>
                  <image href="../Images/50_kva_convert_from_dual_mains_to_single_mains_install_busbar_assembly_120mm_0000110490.svg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View of the UPS Cabinet with the Busbar Assembly for
Single Mains Installed</title>
                  <image href="../Images/50_kva_convert_installed_Fview_120mm_0000110489.svg"
                         scalefit="yes"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
      </ol>
